<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://proletaricomunisti.blogspot.com/2023/02/pc-12-febbraio-riprendere-e-far.html'>pc 12 febbraio: Riprendere e far circolare il volantino diffuso ieri alla manifestazione di Milano. Alcune foto</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-5407749332482872387' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<p style="text-align: center;">&nbsp;<a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv00e_xLPEk89eSrmckClUP6t0rlO0XfaP_BvZYjK3drPOHz668Ob2p8aHFObSnnSGfrZsIw2Vg1KkLZ1eGBL2pjOyNpMAyzDZ_se8sP_A_C3UPCY8YlAsi5yJB1mD5wsSVbG1ESFgnAXhTwjg7UYKrfC4f_PQRXLjjyOm9upcwLfLLEZRvtT2-oZ1Dw/s1550/cospito%2011%20febbraio_page-0001.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="1550" data-original-width="1119" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhv00e_xLPEk89eSrmckClUP6t0rlO0XfaP_BvZYjK3drPOHz668Ob2p8aHFObSnnSGfrZsIw2Vg1KkLZ1eGBL2pjOyNpMAyzDZ_se8sP_A_C3UPCY8YlAsi5yJB1mD5wsSVbG1ESFgnAXhTwjg7UYKrfC4f_PQRXLjjyOm9upcwLfLLEZRvtT2-oZ1Dw/w462-h640/cospito%2011%20febbraio_page-0001.jpg" width="462" /></a></p><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhwS0IsOZsGs_xM8m7WizP406PdHWlhANn-cfTjbCCb_J35JCak0apLN-cKi0Wf9tgXGERpjjYEFwBbYBa5SIiQyqGiqJCMEMvvaBQNq74-14hUBtpLB3aVX--t-YtfKfPoshbQnLJqksJhEwphBNOIlPObPHhIBAtbvueMyPWKbgjQZGjUun9tav9GDg/s1600/mi%2011%20a.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="1200" data-original-width="1600" height="300" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhwS0IsOZsGs_xM8m7WizP406PdHWlhANn-cfTjbCCb_J35JCak0apLN-cKi0Wf9tgXGERpjjYEFwBbYBa5SIiQyqGiqJCMEMvvaBQNq74-14hUBtpLB3aVX--t-YtfKfPoshbQnLJqksJhEwphBNOIlPObPHhIBAtbvueMyPWKbgjQZGjUun9tav9GDg/w400-h300/mi%2011%20a.jpg" width="400" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgdbLQuBqixW_Lgfnusf00bNwEXZV4QD6Gq8WDrORxYpq5kYpas0l9YsszQOZ2Ln69_Br-U9JTRwtZ9vOVSXzAcIKQyIPmbj8BCWSTk_mdZ6PNsDzB9Z_NvK82HTIhLvrL2z2f7q9ZSBRC8MW2wX0xKWzOjfivq-LCAywH-tYdrnUT3i-0JpL9l5LNwTg/s1600/mi%2011%20b.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img